document_notes.text:
This update for rubygem-actionpack-5_1 fixes the following issues:

- CVE-2020-8164: Possible Strong Parameters Bypass in ActionPack.
  There is a strong parameters bypass vector in ActionPack.
  (bsc#1172177)
